            .</p>
               <p>Q. Had your house any occasion on the 5th of August last to send to Mr. Hatsell any money - A. They had, they sent 100 l in bank post bills.</p>
               <p>Q. Did you obtain the bank post bills - A. No, I entered the notes from 3874 up to 3884 each of the 5th of August payable to 
               <persName id="t18090920-97-person1001">
                  John 
                  Hatsell
               <interp inst="t18090920-97-person1001" type="surname" value="Hatsell"></interp>
