                  </persName>
            , ESQ. Q. We understand this letter was addressed to you, did you receive this letter - A. No.</p>
               <p>Q. You would have received on the 5th of August at night - A. I should, I did not receive it on that evening, nor on the next morning.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18090920-97-person1006">
